title: Dreadknight Garen free skin not working??
body: So I just recently managed to get the free Dreadknight Garen code, but whenever I try to redeem it, it shows "There was a problem fulfilling your store items, please try again". I just started playing and Garen was a pretty nice champion so I would like to equip a skin. Any luck?? Thanks!

replies.body: Looks like someone might have been able to get that skin added for you in a ticket or something, I'm showing Dreadknight Garen already added to your account earlier today ^_^! Let me know if you still can't see him anywhere though!
I see it now, thank you so much!! <3
